1
00:00:10,176 --> 00:00:10,877
Come here.

2
00:00:10,877 --> 00:00:11,877
Let's see the mission.

3
00:00:12,245 --> 00:00:14,080
What is it?

4
00:00:14,914 --> 00:00:16,249
Before you check that,

5
00:00:16,750 --> 00:00:18,070
don't you want to get down first?

6
00:00:19,886 --> 00:00:21,153
Mission objective:

7
00:00:21,154 --> 00:00:22,489
Both parties...

8
00:00:23,723 --> 00:00:24,957
Having the time of your life?

9
00:00:24,958 --> 00:00:26,191
Even though we're both guys,

10
00:00:26,192 --> 00:00:27,327
I can't stand...

11
00:00:41,941 --> 00:00:43,175
Is the shot clear?

12
00:00:43,176 --> 00:00:44,243
Not really.

13
00:00:44,244 --> 00:00:46,312
That'll make for a better headline anyway.

14
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:47,947
Whatever...

15
00:00:47,948 --> 00:00:49,783
Let the managers handle the communication.

16
00:00:50,216 --> 00:00:51,985
They're probably more worried than we are.

17
00:00:57,223 --> 00:00:58,825
Mission objective:

18
00:00:59,626 --> 00:01:00,859
Each person

19
00:01:00,860 --> 00:01:02,529
must share three secrets.

20
00:01:02,862 --> 00:01:03,929
The secrets must be true

21
00:01:03,930 --> 00:01:05,064
and never told before.

22
00:01:11,638 --> 00:01:12,806
Oh, please.

23
00:01:12,831 --> 00:01:14,271
They're called secrets for a reason.

24
00:01:14,541 --> 00:01:16,421
Once you say them, they
aren't secrets anymore.

25
00:01:16,776 --> 00:01:17,776
True.

26
00:01:17,777 --> 00:01:19,297
We could just text them to each other.

27
00:01:20,647 --> 00:01:21,647
Oh, right!

28
00:01:21,848 --> 00:01:22,948
You're so smart.

29
00:01:22,949 --> 00:01:23,583
Here...

30
00:01:23,850 --> 00:01:24,484
Wait, did we ever

31
00:01:24,485 --> 00:01:25,518
exchange contact info?

32
00:01:28,655 --> 00:01:29,655
Let's add each other.

33
00:01:30,957 --> 00:01:32,826
What's "BY"?

34
00:01:34,027 --> 00:01:35,128
My initials.

35
00:01:36,096 --> 00:01:37,629
That's so boring.

36
00:01:37,630 --> 00:01:39,532
Can't you pick something more unique?

37
00:01:39,966 --> 00:01:41,333
You mean like

38
00:01:41,334 --> 00:01:42,802
"Bai-Bai-Bai-Bai"?

39
00:01:43,336 --> 00:01:44,737
Hey, it's easy to remember!

40
00:01:46,339 --> 00:01:47,040
Fine.

41
00:01:47,273 --> 00:01:48,508
Let's type the first one.

42
00:01:49,109 --> 00:01:50,142
Don't let them see.

43
00:01:50,143 --> 00:01:51,344
Let's make them jealous.

44
00:01:55,259 --> 00:01:56,939
[Bai: I need to sleep with a stuffed doll]

45
00:01:59,622 --> 00:02:01,309
[I can't sleep without taking a shower]

46
00:02:01,988 --> 00:02:03,689
That's not a secret.

47
00:02:03,690 --> 00:02:05,291
You just said it out loud.

48
00:02:05,692 --> 00:02:06,792
Well, the rules didn't say

49
00:02:06,793 --> 00:02:08,033
who it had to be a secret from.

50
00:02:09,395 --> 00:02:10,096
Okay...

51
00:02:10,296 --> 00:02:11,296
Number two.

52
00:02:13,971 --> 00:02:15,332
[Bai: Really bad sleep posture]

53
00:02:15,357 --> 00:02:17,079
[I'm extremely lazy in the mornings]

54
00:02:18,037 --> 00:02:19,505
What do you mean you sleep in?

55
00:02:19,506 --> 00:02:21,040
You woke up the second I touched you.

56
00:02:21,508 --> 00:02:23,576
I sleep in on beds, not sofas.

57
00:02:25,178 --> 00:02:26,646
You always have an excuse.

58
00:02:27,447 --> 00:02:28,447
Okay.

59
00:02:28,648 --> 00:02:29,648
Number three.

60
00:02:30,805 --> 00:02:32,565
[Bai: I talk in my sleep]

61
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:33,992
[I like you.]

62
00:02:34,921 --> 00:02:36,089
You like me?
